#version 1
first functional release
#
Gets a list of .txt files in the current directory and ouputs a file with those lines sorted by frequency

put matrix.rb in the directory and then call it with ./matrix.rb
if it doesn't work make sure matrix.rb has execute privledges
matrix will ask what you want the file to be called, then close
